quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,59,Nos sent Noah his people dictus O my people worship DEUS; vos non habet alius deus Eum. Ego fear pro vos retribution awesome feria
  7,60,Dux his people dictus Nos vide vos est far astray
  7,61,He dictus O my people ego est astray; ego est messenger Dominus universe
  7,62,Ego deliver vos messages my Dominus ego advise vos ego know DEUS quod vos non know
  7,63,Est it too much de wonder ut reminder advenit vos tuus Dominus vir vos warn vos lead vos to righteousness ut vos attain mercy
  7,64,They rejected eum. Consequently nos saved eum those eum in ark nos drowned those rejected noster revelations; they est blind